# .assetsignore — Cloudflare Workers static-assets ignore list (gitignore-style syntax).
# Adopted from clint-engine/templates/assetsignore (the canonical list — see
# clint-engine/docs/CONTRACTS.md "Templates & tools"). Keeps dev-only files, source control,
# and editable art masters out of the deployed bundle.
#
# engine/core and engine/phaser (incl. the vendored Phaser build) DO ship — the game imports
# them at runtime. Nothing under engine/ needs excluding here: the vendored copy sync-engine.mjs
# writes carries no test/docs/tooling paths (clint-engine's own test/ and docs/ live at ITS repo
# root, outside the engine/ directory that actually gets copied into this repo).

**/.wrangler
**/node_modules
**/.git
**/.DS_Store
**/.env
.claude
*.zip
*.md
wrangler.toml
.assetsignore
voice
tools/
docs/
art/img/*.png
